data.description: OPEN HOUSE on 01/06/24 and 01/07/24 from 12:00 P.M. - 3:00 P.M.    Welcome to Your Oasis in the Heart of Leon Valley. Nestled amidst the tranquility of towering trees in an oversized lot, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans 1644 square feet in the heart of Leon Valley presents an exceptional blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting recent renovations, this residence offers a seamless fusion of modern upgrades and serene surroundings.    Notable Features:  Within the past two years, this home has undergone substantial upgrades, ensuring longevity and durability. A newly replaced metal roof stands as a testament to quality and longevity, offering peace of mind for years to come. Replacing the windows has not only enhanced the aesthetics but also improved energy efficiency. Additionally, the installation of an awning and gutters further adds to the home's functionality and curb appeal. Complete with an extended driveway, irrigation system and gas fireplace, this home is ready to move-in.   Unique Aspects:  Surrounded by stately trees, this property provides a sense of natural seclusion and privacy. The lush greenery and mature trees not only offer shade and beauty but create a peaceful ambiance, making it a haven from the bustling city life.    The Leon Valley Experience:  Situated in the City of Leon Valley, this residence enjoys a prime location, serving as a gateway to San Antonio's premier attractions. With attractions like Sea World and Six Flags Fiesta Texas a mere nine miles away, residents revel in easy access to entertainment and leisure options. Bandera Road and Loop 410 provide seamless connectivity to these attractions and the thriving northwest employment base. Moreover, being just three miles from the Medical District and a short eight-mile drive to the San Antonio International Airport, convenience is a hallmark of living in Leon Valley.    This is your opportunity to embrace the perfect balance between serene living and accessibility to the vibrant offerings of San Antonio. Schedule a visit today and experience the charm and convenience this home has to offer.
